# Restaurant Management API

Production-ready Restaurant Management System built using Golang.

## Features

- JWT Authentication
- Role Based Access
- User Management
- Menu Management
- Order APIs
- Payment APIs
- Inventory APIs
- Swagger Documentation
- Docker Support
- Redis Cache
- PostgreSQL
- Logging
- Environment Variables
- Graceful Shutdown
- Unit Testing

## Tech Stack

- Golang
- Gin
- PostgreSQL
- Redis
- Docker
- Swagger
- JWT
- bcrypt
- Makefile

## Project Structure

cmd/
internal/
pkg/
configs/
database/
docs/
scripts/

## Installation

git clone ...

go mod download

go run cmd/server/main.go

## API Documentation

/swagger/index.html

